name: Opus VII Booster Box
extDescription:
Opus VII adds new titles to the game, including Final Fantasy Crystal Chronicles: Ring of Fates, Final Fantasy Legends, and Final Fantasy Brave Exvius. There will be popular characters added to the series, and new original art from Final Fantasy veteran artists: Toshiyuki Itahana (Final Fantasy Crystal Chronicles: Ring of Fates ), Akira Oguro (Final Fantasy Legends), Kumiko Koike (Final Fantasy (Various Monsters)), and Toshitaka Matsuda (Final Fantasy).

Strengthen your FINAL FANTASY TRADING CARD GAME deck with one of our BOOSTER PACKS!

Booster packs include:
• 12 cards total
• 1 premium foiled card
• 36 packs per booster box
